title: Ep - 151 - JENNIFER AYDIN FROM REAL HOUSEWIVES OF NEW JERSEY
description:
Kate’s daughter Hayes gives a rundown of her favorite reality tv shows. 


Jennifer Aydin from Real Housewives of New Jersey discusses her life before Bravo, how she was cast for the show, and the dramatic moments from this wild season. 


Sondra Celli’s over-the-top wedding dresses have been showcased on My Big Fat American Gypsy Wedding, and earlier on the spinoff series, Gypsy Sisters. She explains how she began her career, how reality television producers found her, and behind the scenes of gypsy weddings. 


Celebrity makeup and hair stylist Tarryn Feldman helps Kate review Real Housewives of Beverly Hills and this season’s adopted dog debacle.
